cu.explanation_en: Setting local SCTP control port to 0 (invalid port) will cause F1 interface binding failure and connection issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting local N control port to 0 (invalid port) will cause F1 interface binding failure and connection issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地 N 控制端口設定為 0（無效端口）將導致 F1 介面綁定失敗和連線問題。
